<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <title>Taepyung Company Profile - 05</title>

  <style>
    @page {
      size: A4 landscape;
      margin: 0;
    }

    :root {
      --green: #387040;
      --light-green: #70C088;
      --cream: #F7F5EF;
      --black: #111111;
      --gray: #777777;
      --line: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html,
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Noto Sans KR", sans-serif;
      background: #d9d9d9;
      color: var(--black);
      -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
      print-color-adjust: exact;
    }

    .page {
      position: relative;
      width: 297mm;
      height: 210mm;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20mm 22mm 16mm;
      background: var(--cream);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* Header */
    .topbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      height: 14mm;
      margin-bottom: 18mm;
    }

    .logo-area {
      width: 42mm;
      height: 12mm;
      border: 1px dashed rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.35);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 8px;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .logo-area img {
      width: 100%;
      max-height: 100%;
      object-fit: contain;
      display: block;
    }

    .doc-label {
      padding-top: 1mm;
      font-size: 8px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      color: var(--gray);
      text-align: right;
    }

    /* Main Layout */
    .layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.82fr 1.18fr;
      gap: 22mm;
      height: 128mm;
    }

    .left,
    .right {
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .left {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      font-size: 8.5px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 9mm;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 30px;
      line-height: 1.16;
      letter-spacing: -0.065em;
      font-weight: 760;
    }

    .lead {
      margin-top: 12mm;
      max-width: 84mm;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.85;
      letter-spacing: -0.035em;
      color: #222;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    /* Bottom Summary */
    .summary-box {
      width: 82mm;
      border-top: 1.5px solid var(--green);
      padding-top: 5.5mm;
    }

    .summary-title {
      font-size: 25px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.06em;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 780;
      margin-bottom: 4mm;
    }

    .summary-text {
      max-width: 70mm;
      font-size: 10px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: #444;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    /* Business Cards */
    .business-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 5mm;
      margin-bottom: 8mm;
    }

    .business-card {
      min-height: 45mm;
      padding: 7mm;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.68);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .business-card.primary {
      background: var(--green);
      border-color: var(--green);
      color: #fff;
    }

    .business-index {
      font-size: 8px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 8mm;
    }

    .business-card.primary .business-index {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
    }

    .business-title {
      margin: 0 0 4mm;
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: -0.055em;
      font-weight: 760;
    }

    .business-desc {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 10px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: #444;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .business-card.primary .business-desc {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
    }

    /* Structure Bar */
    .structure {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 14mm 1fr 14mm 1fr;
      align-items: center;
      height: 30mm;
      padding: 0 6mm;
      background: rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.16);
    }

    .structure-item {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .structure-label {
      font-size: 8px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 3mm;
    }

    .structure-text {
      font-size: 10px;
      line-height: 1.45;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: #222;
      font-weight: 650;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .arrow {
      width: 100%;
      height: 1px;
      background: rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.45);
      position: relative;
    }

    .arrow::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      right: 0;
      top: 50%;
      width: 5px;
      height: 5px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.55);
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.55);
      transform: translateY(-50%) rotate(45deg);
    }

    /* Footer */
    .footer {
      position: absolute;
      left: 22mm;
      right: 22mm;
      bottom: 9mm;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-end;
      font-size: 7.5px;
      line-height: 1.45;
      color: var(--gray);
    }

    .footer-logo {
      font-weight: 750;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: var(--green);
    }

    .page-no {
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.65);
    }

    @media print {
      html,
      body {
        width: 297mm;
        height: 210mm;
        background: #fff;
      }

      .page {
        margin: 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <section class="page">

    <header class="topbar">
      <div class="logo-area">
        LOGO
        <!-- 로고 넣을 때 -->
        <!-- <img src="assets/taepyung-logo-green.svg" alt="Taepyung"> -->
      </div>

      <div class="doc-label">
        Company Profile<br />
        Ver. 2025-V1
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="layout">

      <section class="left">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">Business Area</div>

          <h1>
            제조, 유통,<br />
            브랜드 운영을 연결하는<br />
            생활 위생지 비즈니스
          </h1>

          <p class="lead">
            태평제지는 생활 위생지 제조 역량을 기반으로 B2B 납품과
            B2C 온라인 판매 채널을 함께 운영하며, 브론디 브랜드를 통해
            소비자 접점을 확장하고 있습니다.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="summary-box">
          <div class="summary-title">Integrated</div>
          <div class="summary-text">
            제품 생산부터 유통, 브랜드 운영, 고객 접점까지
            하나의 흐름으로 연결된 운영 구조를 갖추고 있습니다.
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="right">

        <div class="business-grid">

          <div class="business-card primary">
            <div>
              <div class="business-index">01</div>
              <h3 class="business-title">Manufacturing</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="business-desc">
              두루마리 화장지, 점보롤, 페이퍼타올, 키친타올 등
              생활 위생지 제품군을 제조합니다.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="business-card">
            <div>
              <div class="business-index">02</div>
              <h3 class="business-title">Distribution</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="business-desc">
              공공기관, 기업, 대량 납품 등 다양한 수요처에
              안정적으로 제품을 공급합니다.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="business-card">
            <div>
              <div class="business-index">03</div>
              <h3 class="business-title">Brand</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="business-desc">
              생활 위생지 브랜드 브론디를 중심으로
              제품 경험과 브랜드 인지도를 확장합니다.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="business-card">
            <div>
              <div class="business-index">04</div>
              <h3 class="business-title">Online Channel</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="business-desc">
              쿠팡, 네이버, 카카오 등 온라인 채널을 통해
              소비자 접점을 강화하고 있습니다.
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>

        <div class="structure">
          <div class="structure-item">
            <div class="structure-label">Produce</div>
            <div class="structure-text">제품 제조</div>
          </div>

          <div class="arrow"></div>

          <div class="structure-item">
            <div class="structure-label">Supply</div>
            <div class="structure-text">납품 · 유통</div>
          </div>

          <div class="arrow"></div>

          <div class="structure-item">
            <div class="structure-label">Connect</div>
            <div class="structure-text">브랜드 · 고객 접점</div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </section>

    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="footer-logo">TAE PYEONG PAPER</div>
      <div class="page-no">05</div>
    </footer>

  </section>

</body>
</html>
